      "Popular choices for Highlands Ranch include GAF Timberline HDZ (Class 4, excellent wind resistance, most popular residential shingle in the country), Owens Corning Duration FLEX (Class 4, SureNail technology, premium warranty), Malarkey Vista AR (Class 4, SBS modified asphalt, great for temperature swings), and CertainTeed Presidential Impact (Class 4, premium designer profile, heavyweight construction).",
