    metaTitle: "Castle Rock Roofing Guide: Hail, Wind, and Mountain Weather",
    metaDescription: "Castle Rock roofing guide covering hail damage, extreme wind, mountain weather patterns, and how to protect your home with the right materials and contractor.",
    targetKeyword: "Castle Rock roofing guide",
